

Infortrend Appoints Digiworld Corporation as Their Newest Vietnam Distributor





 
Infortrend Appoints Digiworld Corporation as Their Newest Vietnam Distributor
New Taipei City, Taiwan, [insert date] 2016 – Infortrend® Technology, Inc. (TWSE: 2495) today announced the appointment of Digiworld Corporation as its newest official distribution partner in Vietnam. Together with Infortrend, they aim to bring better and more diverse storage solutions into the Vietnamese market in order to better fulfill its user demands.
As one of the biggest storage distributors in Vietnam, Digiworld Corporation is dedicated to delivering industry-proven storage solutions, and as such will distribute the whole range of Infortrend systems, including the acclaimed EonStor DS family. These award winning storage solutions will provide users not only one of the world’s best price-performance ratios, but also comprehensive data services, simple management and deployment, high availability, flexible scalability, and long term reliability. 
“With Infortrend’s expertise in award winning products, we can offer our customers truly great storage solutions to meet their increasingly complex requirements. We look forward to working together with Infortrend to create a successful partnership for all involved.” said Mr. Doan Hong Viet, CEO at Digiworld Corporation
“We are delighted to collaborate with Digiworld Corporation as an Asia channel partner to help us deliver our products and solutions to customers in their market. We are confident this will be a beneficial partnership and we look forward to achieving success together.” said Victor Chiang, Pan Asia Sales Director at Infortrend.
 
About Digiworld Corporation
Established in 1997, Digiworld, one of 3 biggest ICT distributors in Vietnam, is strong with state-of-the-art IT system and the group of veteran in market analysis, marketing, sales, logistics and after sales service, who can provide the top quality market penetration and market expansion immediately and fully. Over 18 years of trust, Digiworld has been the Authorized Distributor of IT and mobility product for more than 24 world famous brands.
Digiwold is listed in Top 50 Vietnam Brand from UK’s Brand Finance.
Digiworld has a nationwide cover 63 provinces distribution channel of 6000 Resellers. For more information, please visit: www.digiworld.com.vn
 
About Infortrend
Infortrend (TWSE: 2495) has been developing and manufacturing storage solutions for businesses and organizations since 1993. Innovation joins impeccable quality thanks to a passionate team of professionals and an emphasis on in-house design, testing, and manufacturing. Infortrend storage delivers performance and scalability with the latest standards, backed by user friendly data services, personal after-sales support, and unmatched value. Core product families are EonStor DS, EonNAS, and ESVA. For more Information, please visit www.infortrend.com

 
Media Contact:
Nicole Yu
Tel: 886-2-2226-0126 ext 8548
Email: nicole.yu@infortrend.com







