Introduction





						Introduction					


 
CÔNG TY CỔ PHẦN THẾ GIỚI SỐ - DIGIWORLD CORPORATION
Digiworld Corporation (Digiworld) is a leading Distributor for high quality IT and advanced 3C products in Vietnam, listed in VNR500 (Top 500 biggest companies based on the revenue in Vietnam) continuously from 2007 to 2014.












In 2014, Digiworld has achieved USD 230 millions, increased 60% compared to 2013.
Digiworld is now the Authorized Distributor of IT and mobility product for the world famous brands such as: Acer, Asus, HP, Dell, Toshiba, Samsung, Gateway, Genius, Logitech, Belkin, APC, Lenovo, Fuji Xerox, Nokia, Alcatel, Lenovo, AOC, Ricoh, Wiko, Obi Worldphone, CINK TAB, Apple, BenQ, Rapoo. With a nationwide cover 63 provinces distribution channel of 6000 Resellers, Supply Chain system managed by SAP, ERP, Digiworld is proud to bring to the Vietnamese consumers the advanced technologies and products in a cost effective way.
Digiworld is actively realizing the Mission “ELEVATING VIETNAM – Nothing is impossible”.
Visit us at www.digiworld.com.vn
 


 


 



 








































































































 






